        <Parent_String>glassworking equipment [300163223], equipment by material processed [300168082], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
